reviews.review_text: Great recording, great show! Really live, but clear, recording of an exciting show.  Don't let the multiple patches throw you, they're short.  Truly a recording where a board is justly relegated to the role of a patch source.  Nice one!

24 years ago today This is a great show. Anytime there's a Shakedown opener and a Terrapin it's 5 stars for me. Jerry delivers the goods, Brent's singing was stellar but Bob seemed a little under the weather or something, just not as wild as usual. But this show is solid. The AUD recording is excellent, patches and all.
